    "We will thus assume that the amplitude for the 2 → 3 scattering process iM 1 ′ 2 ′ k←12 is already expressed in terms of a basis of master integrals, and focus here on how to incorporate the Cut 1 ′ 2 ′ term at the level of these master integrals.",
